title: A 13-year-old was behind the wheel in Texas crash that killed 9 people and left two University of the Southwest golfers critically injured - CNN
content:

description: A 13-year-old child was behind the wheel of a pickup truck involved in a head-on collision in Texas that killed nine people -- including six University of the Southwest golfers and their coach, National Transportation Safety Board Vice Chairman Bruce Landsberg said Thursday.
